{"title":"红花开在○五线","authors":["晏明"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红花开在○五线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晏明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宣传鼓动员"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在烈日下面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在暴风雨里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她放下扁担，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又举起笔杆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她把好消息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传遍咱工地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"写完好诗篇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又写小快板。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在烈日下面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在暴风雨里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她放下笔杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又扛起扁担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红花开在○五线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红花开在○五线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好汉就在咱眼前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产党员李兆先，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铲土呵，快如飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挑土呵，轻似燕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在装料台上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一筐一筐砂石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一篮一篮鲜花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"砂石堆满四支线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花怒放在心间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一筐一筐砂石，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一篮一篮鲜花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把砂石装满斗车，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把鲜花献给大坝。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}